{
  "_id": "LBrnB5Ncpcb5oryt",
  "name": "Shroud of Vermin",
  "type": "feat",
  "img": "systems/pf1/icons/skills/green_23.jpg",
  "data": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>At 9th level,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/bestiary/rules-for-monsters/creature-types#TOC-Swarm\">swarms</a>&nbsp;no longer see you as prey. You can walk among&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/bestiary/rules-for-monsters/creature-types#TOC-Swarm\">swarms</a>&nbsp;without&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/magic/all-spells/f/fear\">fear</a>&nbsp;of being harmed by them at all, and by taking a&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/gamemastering/combat#TOC-Standard-Actions\">standard action</a>&nbsp;to mentally&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/magic/all-spells/c/command\">command</a>&nbsp;a&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/bestiary/rules-for-monsters/creature-types#TOC-Swarm\">swarm</a>&nbsp;in which you stand, you can direct that&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/bestiary/rules-for-monsters/creature-types#TOC-Swarm\">swarm’s</a>&nbsp;attacks and movements as long as you have more&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/basics-ability-scores/glossary#TOC-Hit-Dice-HD-\">Hit Dice</a>&nbsp;than the&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/bestiary/rules-for-monsters/creature-types#TOC-Swarm\">swarm</a>. Even when you aren’t standing amid a&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/bestiary/rules-for-monsters/creature-types#TOC-Swarm\">swarm</a>, your body crawls with&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/bestiary/rules-for-monsters/creature-types#TOC-Vermin\">vermin</a>, and their chitinous bodies increase your&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/basics-ability-scores/glossary#TOC-Natural-Armor-Bonus\">natural armor bonus</a>&nbsp;by +1. At 11th level, this bonus increases to +2, and at 17th level it increases to +3.</p>"
    },
